{"type":"message","id":"906203d9","parentId":"13e3534d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:24:46.701Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_oqaczigb4dpc_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4483\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2353\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[master ed7d7ca] pulse: 2026-03-24 152414\n 5 files changed, 313 insertions(+), 103 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 152414.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 152414.mutation\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 152414 - The CFI compression experiment identified that binary thresholds (CFI � 0.7 AND freq < 60) fail because \"constant format\" tokens like \"pulse\" (freq=160, CFI=1) look causal but aren't. The next step is to implement and test the hybrid scoring formula: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120).\r\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"plaid-shore","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4483\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2353\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[master ed7d7ca] pulse: 2026-03-24 152414\n 5 files changed, 313 insertions(+), 103 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 152414.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 152414.mutation\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 152414 - The CFI compression experiment identified that binary thresholds (CFI � 0.7 AND freq < 60) fail because \"constant format\" tokens like \"pulse\" (freq=160, CFI=1) look causal but aren't. The next step is to implement and test the hybrid scoring formula: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120).\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774380286698}}
